<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <strong>[Jobs.MakeSense]</strong>
    <h1><%= @title %></h1>
    <strong>Congratulation !</strong>
    <p>You created a new job that makesense.<br/>
      You have 42 days left before this ad goes offline.</p>
    <p>
      You can edit/publish your job ad at any time here:<br/>
      (Please note that it won't reset the 42 days period)<br/>
      <%= @edit_url %>
    </p>
    <p>
      <%= @company.empty? ? "Are you" : "#{@company.capitalize} is" %> looking for the perfect match?<br/>
      Then share this link in your network to reach him/her.<br/>
      <%= @job_url %>
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you for creating a job and have a great day!</p>
    </p>
    <p>
      ~ Emilien
    </p>
    <a href='http://dev-mksjobs.herokuapp.com'>Jobs.MakeSense</a>

  </body>
</html>
